These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
There 4 different types of food: strawberry, spinach, cherry, cauliflower
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, aristoff, bongani, havana
1. the havana-smoker is on the left of the person eating cherry##1
2. the person eating strawberry is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1
3. the person eating cauliflower is in an odd position##4
4. the bongani-smoker is on the left or right of the havana-smoker##3
5. the person eating strawberry is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Food   | strawberry | spinach | cauliflower | cherry |
| Cigar        | dannemann | aristoff   | havana | bongani    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, basketball, skateboarding, golf
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, december, august, october
1. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
3. the person who's birthday is in august is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's birthday is in september is the person who's sport is soccer##1
5. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
6. the person who's birthday is in september is the person who's sport is soccer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Sport   | skateboarding | soccer  | basketball  | golf |
| Birthday   | october    | september | august | december    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: chestnut, lilac, mauve, apricot
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, old-henry, pall-mall, chaman
1. the person who likes apricot is on the left or right of the chaman-smoker##3
2. the person who likes mauve is in an even position##4
3. the chaman-smoker is on the left or right of the person who likes lilac##3
4. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1
5. the davidoff-smoker is in an odd position##4
6. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Color          | apricot | mauve | lilac    | chestnut      |
| Cigar   | pall-mall        | chaman     | davidoff | old-henry |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, june, december, july
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, old-henry, baccarat, ritmeester
1. the person who's birthday is in june is between the cain-smoker and the ritmeester-smoker##2
2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
3. the baccarat-smoker is in an odd position##4
4. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1
5. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Birthday         | july | october | june | december |
| Cigar   | baccarat       | cain   | old-henry    | ritmeester  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, sprite, hot-chocolate, almond-milk
There are 4 different favourite colors: amber, grey, coral, ivory
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person who likes ivory##1
2. the person who likes grey is the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person who likes coral is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an odd position##4
6. the person who likes amber is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | sprite  | fanta    | hot-chocolate   | almond-milk       |
| Color   | amber | ivory | coral | grey |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, almond-milk, milk, cola
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, november, july, may
1. the person who's birthday is in november is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
3. the person drinking milk is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
5. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | milk      | almond-milk | cola | soy-milk |
| Birthday   | may | november     | october  | july  |

