.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-7::.
House: cottage, farmhouse, wooden, craftsman
There are 4 different favourite colors: aquamarine, lilac, blood-red, orange
1. the person who likes orange is in an odd position##4
2. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1
3. the craftsman house is on the left of the wooden house##1
4. the person who likes orange is the cottage house##1
5. the craftsman house is on the left or right of the person who likes aquamarine##3
6. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| House   | cottage | craftsman | wooden | farmhouse    |
| Color     | orange | blood-red  | aquamarine     | lilac |

