.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
City: edinburgh, london, liverpool, boston
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, helicopter, motorbike, bus
1. the person driving the bus is on the left or right of the person traveling to london##3
2. the person traveling to boston is in an odd position##4
3. the person driving the bus is on the left or right of the person traveling to boston##3
4. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
5. the person traveling to edinburgh is between the person traveling to boston and the person traveling to london##2
6. the person driving the helicopter is in an odd position##4
7. the person driving the helicopter is between the person traveling to edinburgh and the person driving the motorbike##2
8. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left or right of the person traveling to london##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| City   | london | edinburgh      | boston | liverpool |
| Transport   | quad-bike  | bus | helicopter    | motorbike            |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-9::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, lemonade, hot-chocolate, tea
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, d&b, metal, salsa
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
2. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
3. the fan of trance is between the fan of d&b and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
4. the fan of trance is in an odd position##4
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the fan of metal##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | tea | lemonade   | 7up | hot-chocolate |
| Music-Genre    | salsa     | d&b | trance     | metal  |

