.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: purple, pink, brown, amber
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, helicopter, airplane, motorbike
1. the person who likes purple is the person driving the motorbike##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
3. the person driving the motorbike is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person who likes brown##2
4. the person who likes purple is in an odd position##4
5. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3
6. the person who likes pink is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Color      | pink       | brown   | purple | amber |
| Transport   | airplane | helicopter | motorbike        | quad-bike    |

