.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, german, mexican, canadian
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, indie, dubstep, canadian-polo
1. the fan of soul is in an even position##4
2. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the brazilian##1
3. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the fan of canadian-polo##1
4. the fan of canadian-polo is on the left of the mexican##1
5. the german is on the left or right of the mexican##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| Nationality   | brazilian   | canadian   | german      | mexican      |
| Music-Genre      | indie | dubstep | canadian-polo | soul |

