.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-12::.
4 different games are played: snooker, monopoly, scrabble, billiard
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, oliveros, pall-mall, dunhill
1. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
2. the pall-mall-smoker is in an even position##4
3. the person playing monopoly is in an even position##4
4. the person playing snooker is on the far right##1
5. the person playing scrabble is between the oliveros-smoker and the pall-mall-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Game          | billiard | monopoly  | scrabble  | snooker |
| Cigar   | dunhill  | pall-mall | bongani | oliveros   |

