.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-13::.
City: hamburg, marseilles, paris, miami
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, august, june, march
1. the person who's birthday is in august is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
3. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left or right of the person traveling to hamburg##3
4. the person traveling to marseilles is in an odd position##4
5. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |     4     |
| City   | marseilles | hamburg | paris | miami  |
| Birthday     | august   | february  | march  | june |

