.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-14::.
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, argentine, russian, mexican
There are 4 different favourite colors: pink, white, emerald, purple
1. the person who likes emerald is in an odd position##4
2. the chinese is in an odd position##4
3. the mexican is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
4. the person who likes pink is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
5. the chinese is on the left or right of the argentine##3
6. the person who likes pink is on the left or right of the person who likes purple##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |      4       |
| Nationality   | russian | mexican | chinese | argentine |
| Color           | purple     | pink     | emerald   | white         |

