.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-15::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: iris, orchid, balloon-flower, amaryllis
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, motorbike, ship, subway
1. the person who growsiris is between the person driving the snowmobile and the person who growsorchid##2
2. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
4. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
5. the person driving the subway is in an odd position##4
6. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |       3       |      4       |
| Flower   | amaryllis | orchid         | iris   | balloon-flower |
| Transport   | ship    | motorbike | subway | snowmobile   |

