.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-16::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, indonesian, colombian, brazilian
House: colonial, cape-cod, wooden, ranch-style
1. the ranch-style house is the colombian##1
2. the wooden house is the american##1
3. the cape-cod house is the brazilian##1
4. the colombian is on the left or right of the brazilian##3
5. the american is in an even position##4
6. the colombian is on the right of the wooden house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Nationality   | indonesian | american | colombian    | brazilian |
| House   | colonial   | wooden  | ranch-style | cape-cod     |

