.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-17::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, handball, weightlifting, tennis
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, pop, rock, punk
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in an even position##4
3. the fan of pop is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
4. the fan of rock is on the left or right of the fan of pop##3
5. the fan of pop is between the fan of punk and the fan of rock##2
6. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the fan of punk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Sport         | tennis   | weightlifting | baseball | handball    |
| Music-Genre   | rock | pop  | punk     | electronic |

