.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, subway, bike, train
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, folk, house, hip-hop
1. the fan of folk is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3
3. the person driving the train is on the far left or far right##3
4. the fan of house is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
5. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
6. the fan of house is in an even position##4
7. the fan of gospel is the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Transport   | train | ship    | bike       | subway |
| Music-Genre       | folk  | house | hip-hop | gospel  |

