.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-19::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, blend, bolivar, havana
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, zinnia, tulip, orchid
1. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the havana-smoker##1
2. the person who growstulip is on the left or right of the person who growspoppy##3
3. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
4. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the bolivar-smoker##1
5. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
6. the person who growspoppy is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Cigar   | blend | bolivar | siglo  | havana |
| Flower     | poppy      | tulip       | zinnia | orchid     |

