.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: ivory, brown, amber, green
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, may, october, april
1. the person who likes brown is in an even position##4
2. the person who likes brown is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in january##3
3. the person who's birthday is in may is between the person who likes ivory and the person who's birthday is in january##2
4. the person who likes brown is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who likes green##1
6. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Color         | ivory | amber   | green | brown |
| Birthday   | april          | may | january         | october  |

 